  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/8643f0fbbbb4e8ba663d71ebbc17416b.poster.avif?t=1756369874\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/8643f0fbbbb4e8ba663d71ebbc17416b.webm?t=1756369874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/8643f0fbbbb4e8ba663d71ebbc17416b.mp4?t=1756369874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The JumpKin Adventure Begins!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into a cute yet competitive world! Are you ready to challenge your friends with your pumpkin character? In this vibrant, energy-packed platform game, you’ll experience both fun and strategy at the same time!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from over 10 uniquely designed characters. Which pumpkin will you pick? Select the map and game mode, decide whether abilities will be enabled, and let the game begin!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Modes:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pumpkin Hunt:</strong> In this mode, the goal is to hunt down your opponents and earn points! When one pumpkin lands on another, the latter explodes. The attacking player gains 1 point, while the defeated player loses 1 point. Plan your strategy and use your speed and wits to outplay your rivals!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Crown Chase:</strong> At the start of the game, a crown appears at a specific location on the map! The longer you hold onto the crown, the more points you earn. Be quick—only the best at chasing and escaping will win!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exploding Pumpkins:</strong> In this thrilling mode, a random player starts the game with a bomb. You must pass it to another player before it explodes! Get rid of the bomb before time runs out, or you’ll be the one to explode!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Awesome Power-Ups Await!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect hidden power-ups on the map to gain an advantage! But these powers are random and limited, so choosing the right power at the right time will be part of your strategy. For example:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/9f6bab0731d14d8964f18677d85937d2.poster.avif?t=1756369874\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/9f6bab0731d14d8964f18677d85937d2.webm?t=1756369874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/9f6bab0731d14d8964f18677d85937d2.mp4?t=1756369874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Invisibility:</strong> Move undetected and score points without getting caught!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/ba657833cfef508b412295c3297bcb6e.poster.avif?t=1756369874\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/ba657833cfef508b412295c3297bcb6e.webm?t=1756369874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/ba657833cfef508b412295c3297bcb6e.mp4?t=1756369874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Double Jump:</strong> Overcome obstacles easily and stay ahead of your opponents!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/fce958dba8673193cc22b7286144855c.poster.avif?t=1756369874\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/fce958dba8673193cc22b7286144855c.webm?t=1756369874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/fce958dba8673193cc22b7286144855c.mp4?t=1756369874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Speed Boost:</strong> Nothing can stop you—zip through the map like lightning!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/496827a25f588efccb7ff7a90404b9f3.poster.avif?t=1756369874\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/496827a25f588efccb7ff7a90404b9f3.webm?t=1756369874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/496827a25f588efccb7ff7a90404b9f3.mp4?t=1756369874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Shield:</strong> Strengthen your defense—if an opponent jumps on you, you won’t lose points!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But be careful! These powers have a limited duration, so plan your strategy accordingly and make your move at the right time to gain the upper hand!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the end, whoever collects the most points wins! But it’s not just about winning—it’s about who has the most fun and makes the best memories in this action-packed adventure!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The best way to compete, have fun, and spend time with your friends awaits in <strong>JumpKin Adventure!</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/8643f0fbbbb4e8ba663d71ebbc17416b.poster.avif?t=1756369874\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/8643f0fbbbb4e8ba663d71ebbc17416b.webm?t=1756369874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/8643f0fbbbb4e8ba663d71ebbc17416b.mp4?t=1756369874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The JumpKin Adventure Begins!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into a cute yet competitive world! Are you ready to challenge your friends with your pumpkin character? In this vibrant, energy-packed platform game, you’ll experience both fun and strategy at the same time!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from over 10 uniquely designed characters. Which pumpkin will you pick? Select the map and game mode, decide whether abilities will be enabled, and let the game begin!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Modes:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pumpkin Hunt:</strong> In this mode, the goal is to hunt down your opponents and earn points! When one pumpkin lands on another, the latter explodes. The attacking player gains 1 point, while the defeated player loses 1 point. Plan your strategy and use your speed and wits to outplay your rivals!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Crown Chase:</strong> At the start of the game, a crown appears at a specific location on the map! The longer you hold onto the crown, the more points you earn. Be quick—only the best at chasing and escaping will win!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exploding Pumpkins:</strong> In this thrilling mode, a random player starts the game with a bomb. You must pass it to another player before it explodes! Get rid of the bomb before time runs out, or you’ll be the one to explode!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Awesome Power-Ups Await!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect hidden power-ups on the map to gain an advantage! But these powers are random and limited, so choosing the right power at the right time will be part of your strategy. For example:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/9f6bab0731d14d8964f18677d85937d2.poster.avif?t=1756369874\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/9f6bab0731d14d8964f18677d85937d2.webm?t=1756369874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/9f6bab0731d14d8964f18677d85937d2.mp4?t=1756369874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Invisibility:</strong> Move undetected and score points without getting caught!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/ba657833cfef508b412295c3297bcb6e.poster.avif?t=1756369874\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/ba657833cfef508b412295c3297bcb6e.webm?t=1756369874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/ba657833cfef508b412295c3297bcb6e.mp4?t=1756369874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Double Jump:</strong> Overcome obstacles easily and stay ahead of your opponents!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/fce958dba8673193cc22b7286144855c.poster.avif?t=1756369874\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/fce958dba8673193cc22b7286144855c.webm?t=1756369874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/fce958dba8673193cc22b7286144855c.mp4?t=1756369874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Speed Boost:</strong> Nothing can stop you—zip through the map like lightning!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/496827a25f588efccb7ff7a90404b9f3.poster.avif?t=1756369874\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/496827a25f588efccb7ff7a90404b9f3.webm?t=1756369874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276440/extras/496827a25f588efccb7ff7a90404b9f3.mp4?t=1756369874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Shield:</strong> Strengthen your defense—if an opponent jumps on you, you won’t lose points!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But be careful! These powers have a limited duration, so plan your strategy accordingly and make your move at the right time to gain the upper hand!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the end, whoever collects the most points wins! But it’s not just about winning—it’s about who has the most fun and makes the best memories in this action-packed adventure!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The best way to compete, have fun, and spend time with your friends awaits in <strong>JumpKin Adventure!</strong></p>",
